鮩字的基本解释

鮩
bìng
鮊鱼。

鮩字的汉语字典释义

[①]［bìng］
［《廣韻》蒲迥切，上迥，並。］
［《廣韻》蒲猛切，上梗，並。］
白鱼。

鮩字的康熙字典解释

【亥集中】【魚字部】　鮩； 康熙笔画：17； 页码：页1469第19
【廣韻】蒲猛切【集韻】蒲幸切，?音併。與?同。鮊魚別名。【玉篇】白魚也。又【廣韻】蒲迥切【集韻】部迥切，?音竝。又【集韻】薄必切，音邲。義?同。

[Hai Collection] [Fish Character Department] 　宩; Kangxi Strokes: 17; Page Number: Page 1469 Page 19
[Guang Yun] Pu Meng cut [Ji Yun] Pu Xing cut, and the sound merged. Same as? The alias of 鮊鱼. [Jade articles] White fish too. Also [Guangyun] Pu Jiongqi [Jiyun] The part is completely cut, and the sound is merged. Also 【Jiyun】Thin must cut, with sound. Righteous? Same.
